A reloadable debit card offered to Brazilians that can be funded with either a bank transfer (BRL) or funded with bitcoins.  Over 10,000 locations in Brazil accept this debit card for purchases.

##History

This service was announced on June 21, 2012 (2.1).  The service is offered from Vivar IT.

